      "content": "i know i should ask the doctor but i cant reach them until tomorrow morning and im really struggling to sleep. i wasnt thinking of getting drunk or anything, just like a tiny bit of wine to help the diazepam work more effectively. is it really that dangerous for a single small glass, or is it just a general precaution?",
